{{> header}}
<h1>Your task is due tomorrow</h1>
<p>Hi {{name}}, just a friendly reminder that you have a task due <strong>tomorrow</strong>.</p>
<div class="card">
  <p><strong>Task:</strong> {{taskTitle}}</p>
  <p><strong>Board:</strong> {{boardName}}</p>
  <p><strong>Due date:</strong> {{dueDate}}</p>
</div>
<p style="text-align:center;margin:28px 0;">
  <a href="{{taskUrl}}" class="btn">View task</a>
</p>
<hr>
<p class="small">You're receiving this because this task is assigned to you. You can update your notification preferences in your account settings.</p>
{{> footer}}
